    <briefdescription>
<para>Per-SIMD TU dispatch for RaBitQ flat scanner. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Included after <ref refid="dispatching_8h" kindref="compound">dispatching.h</ref> in each per-SIMD TU, so that ScannerMixIn from <ref refid="dispatching_8h" kindref="compound">dispatching.h</ref> is visible (same TU).</para>
<para>Provides the rabitq_make_knn_scanner_impl&lt;SL&gt; specialization that wraps RaBitQHeapHandler in ScannerMixIn. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
